title: Website for b1MT
body:
We are thinking in developing a website for b1MT, this would be the road map:
1º Step: The web will show all the info, pools to stake and social networks about b1mt, and for sure a link to [1MT](https://1milliontoken.org/)
2º Step: Swap integration to make easier to buy b1MT
3º Step: Integrate governance
...

Question:
Do we want the website for b1MT?
